translation: NOW THE WORDS OF VICTORY ARE RELATED:

gurmukhi: ਜੈ ਸਬਦ ਦੇਵ ਪੁਕਾਰ ਹੀਂ || ਸਭ ਫੂਲ ਫੂਲਨ ਡਾਰ ਹੀਂ ||
transliteration: Jai Sabad Dev Poukaar Hoon|| Sabh Phool Phoolan Daar Hoon||
translation: All the gods are hailing the victory of the goddess and showering the flowers.

gurmukhi: ਘਨਸਾਰ ਕੁੰਕਮ ਲਿਅਾੲਿ ਕੈ || ਟੀਕਾ ਦੀਯੋ ਹਰਖਾੲਿ ਕੈ ||੧||੨੨੦||
transliteration: Ghansaar Kounkam Liaae Kai|| Tikaa Dooyo Harkhaae Kai||1||220||
translation: They brought the saffron and with great delight they applied the mark on their foreheds.1.220.

gurmukhi: ੳੁਸਤਤ ਸਭਹੂੰ ਕਰੀ ਅਪਾਰਾ || ਬ੍ਹਮ ਕਵਚ ਕੋ ਜਾਪ ੳੁਚਾਰਾ ||
transliteration: Oustat Sabh-hoon Daroo Apaaraa|| Brahm Kavach Ko Jaap Ouchaaraa||
translation: All of them extremely eulogized the goddess and repeated the mantra known as “Brahm-Kavach”.

gurmukhi: ਸੰਤ ਸੰਬੂਹ ਪ੍ਰਫੁੱਲਤ ਭੲੇ || ਦੁਸਟ ਅਰਿਸਟ ਨਾਸ ਹੁਅੈ ਗੲੇ ||੨||੨੨੧||
transliteration: Sant Sanbooh Praphullat Bhae|| Doust Arist Naas Huai Gad||2||221||
translation: All the saints were pleased because the tyrants have been destroyed.2.221.

gurmukhi: ਸਾਧਨ ਕੋ ਸੁਖ ਬਢੇ ਅਨੇਕਾ || ਦਾਨਵ ਦੁਸਟ ਨ ਬਾਚਾ ੲੇਕਾ ||
transliteration: Saadhan Ko Soukh Badhe Anekaa|| Daanav Doust Na Baachaa Ekaa||
translation: The comfort of the saints increased in many ways and not even one demon could survive.

gurmukhi: ਸੰਤ ਸਹਾੲਿ ਸਦਾ ਜਗ ਮਾੲੀ || ਜੱਹ ਤੱਹ ਸਾਧਨ ਹੋਹਿ ਸਹਾੲੀ ||੩||੨੨੨||
transliteration: Sant Sahaae Sadaa Jag Maaoo|| Jah Tah Saadhan Hoh(i) Sahaaoo||3||222||
translation: The mother of the universe ever helps the saints and is helpful to them everywhere.3.222.
O Yoga-fire, Enlightener of the Earth! I salute Thee.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ ਸੁੰਭ ਹੰਤੀ ਨਮੋ ਕ੍ਰੂਰ ਕਾਲੰ ||
transliteration: Namo Soubh Hantoo Namo Kroor Kaalan||
translation: O the Destroyer of Sumbh and dreadful manifestation of Death!
O the Destroyer of Dhumar Nain , O the Destroyer of Rakat Beej!
